QuestData.Title: I Drew Aggro...culture
QuestData.Description: $p? Boy am I glad to see ya.$b$bI was tryin' ta ditch that genesaur when I stumbled across this rangari camp.$b$bNext thing I know, the ground is creepin' up and spittin' out all sorts of angry plants.$b$bI barely made it out of me tank before that genesaur threw it like it was an empty beer mug.$b$bI'm gonna make my way back to the road an' look fer me tank.$b$bI'll see ya there when yer done.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Thaelin Darkanvil at the Wildwood Wash.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet Thaelin Darkanvil at the Wildwood Wash.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah perfect. I'll get this up an' runnin' in no time.
